=== EVENT_AUCTION_HOUSE ===
# id: 18
# title: Auction House
# chinese_title: 拍卖行
# category: Trading
# mode: starmap

A luxury liner hosts a traveling auction. Among the lots: ancient navigation data, alien tech, and a mysterious sealed crate.

* [Bid on the navigation data] {requires: credits >= 20}
  ~ gain_item("Star Atlas Fragment")
  导航 (dǎoháng) — navigation
* [Bid on the alien tech] {requires: credits >= 30}
  ~ gain_item("Quantum Stabilizer")
  技术 (jìshù) — technology
* [Just browse and mingle]
  ~ gain_credits(5)
  观看 (guānkàn) — watch
